{"tid":261303,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"免費小組英文補習，aim 5以上適用","createTime":"2017-05-28T10:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T05:46:30.000Z","uid":119023,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3709e4e3f044e8da3a8c27d7a306672e5d33c90","tid":261303,"uid":119023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個暑假未揾唔到intern ，仲等緊消息<br />\n打算義助下dse學生教英文<br />\n<br />\n暫時打算五人一組<br />\n一星期一堂<br />\nAim 得5以上，英文程度應該唔差<br />\n我會教下1d advanced 少少ge技巧<br />\n例如Writing 點polish篇文 、 作文脈絡等等<br />\n其他暫時未諗<br />\n<br />\n一篇自己作ge文<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/185038_4513697ca1fcddccad1478a65e8d882d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F185038_4513697ca1fcddccad1478a65e8d882d.jpg&h=8befdcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/185039_4513697ca1fcddccad1478a65e8d882d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F185039_4513697ca1fcddccad1478a65e8d882d.jpg&h=63f84c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/185039_ae348cd3f6daff61f4adf9b70b1877cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F185039_ae348cd3f6daff61f4adf9b70b1877cd.jpg&h=2752fb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下本人少少資料，讀緊科大<br />\n利申：Dse 英文得5<br />\n打算下年考黎試試自己有冇進步<br />\n<br />\n由於係免費，純粹想幫下dse學生，希望連登仔唔好郁d就屌<br />\n<br />\n私補收費請pm"},{"pid":"bbefbd245766558b9e993df1c60c3a0efb991515","tid":261303,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86033ce1f361fb709434fea493d44e2205cb9a14","tid":261303,"uid":54961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"巴定絲？下年考Dse"},{"pid":"587abead4aa82d0f17e5beb89130aa927d5edefd","tid":261303,"uid":54961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"咩地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f6b9cbfb84314bb9a75202431bbd4c0be46f59","tid":261303,"uid":33390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e6e373613d84ab5f3f16f8a4f019a13385506f7d","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"呢篇野麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1e675e93318c783b2391488a9ecbf6bbf0ac6d","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢篇野麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到你英文真係prove到有進步先再教人啦<br />\n除左家境極清貧，考得公開考試仲同你慳咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"3be52d651eb176286ba8d876d1750e3b2e96edc3","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評。俾負評果個自己google下，睇下人地D範文係寫成點。"},{"pid":"faf4c1a2e55eaa73c03979fa47847e3dab9c21aa","tid":261303,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"理科LV 5都可能適合教個想LV5既人<br />\n<br />\n英文(中文都係) 冇粒星真係唔好教人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就考IELTS 7.5先再教"},{"pid":"349f13fd980991660798d7ecb8ba7474f82e749d","tid":261303,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99d055a1b150ac3cf5b6fe836c844358ebb6a555","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理科LV 5都可能適合教個想LV5既人<br />\n<br />\n英文(中文都係) 冇粒星真係唔好教人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就考IELTS 7.5先再教</blockquote><br />\n我俾過一個AL拎A/ IELTS 8.5的人教英文。如果只係用ＯＰ篇文黎睇，兩者的程度真係差好遠。"},{"pid":"630871be4dc2e428c10ff016eb1e8e2c8c68c793","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心做壞事</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真，免費唔係大曬。高中三年，兩年都用左黎讀ｃｏｎｔｅｎｔ，得返半年多Ｄ黎操卷，緊係想搵個勁人黎教。"},{"pid":"009e291dd9b9468167f3019e119254b3a5cdd019","tid":261303,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e622015dd00e1051407330cdec6a06c266086d5e","tid":261303,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真　你篇文唔少文法錯誤<br />\nProf畀好grade你可能係因為啲points好，而一定唔係字句好</blockquote><br />\nyear1 或者會俾人捉grammar format... etc 濕碎野，但係之後就冇人理呢Ｄ。<br />\n<br />\n佢呢篇或者ref.用得岩，point勁，拎到高分唔出奇，不過高分=/=英文好。"},{"pid":"b3c2c0c1b65821390b30e9ee943c4a3ea23b6d3e","tid":261303,"uid":70743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得好好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421391c0666f6783efa2d2b2ed9cc24411b9ec8c","tid":261303,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"有無野送？"}]}